  "text": "language\nSkip to main content\nPRO\nPro indicator: A premium offering that requires a paid subscription.\nAmson安生｜數位行銷 x IG變現\nHome\nContacts\nAutomation\nManychat AI\nInbox\n2\nSettings\nMy Profile\nHelp\nSettings\nMain\nGeneral\nNotifications\nTeam Members\nLogs\nDisplay\nBilling\nSubscriptions\nInvoices\nPayment Details\nInbox\nInbox Behavior\nAuto-Assignment\nChannels\nInstagram\nTikTok\nWhatsApp\nMessenger\nSMS\nEmail\nTelegram\nAutomation\nFields\nTags\nConversion Events\nExtensions\nAPI\nApps\nIntegrations\nPayments\nInstalled Templates\nPixel\nStripe Account\nConnect Stripe Account\nYou can accept payments via Messenger and Instagram. You need to connect an existing Stripe account or create a new one to access Buy Button in your Automations. Buy Button can be used with Card, Gallery, List or Media Template elements. Learn more\nPayPal Account\nHow can I find needed Client ID and Webhook ID?\nConnect PayPal Account\nYou can accept PayPal payments via Messenger and Instagram. You need to connect an existing PayPal Business account to access Buy Button in your Automation.\nCurrency\nUS Dollar\nEuro\nPound Sterling\nCanadian Dollar\nAustralian Dollar\nBrazilian Real\nHong Kong Dollar\nJapanese Yen\nNew Zealand Dollar\nMexican Peso\nSwiss Franc\nDanish Krone\nNorwegian Krone\nSingapore Dollar\nSwedish Krona\nSouth African Rand\nMalaysian ringgit\nPhilippine peso\nCzech Koruna\nIsraeli New Shekel\nTaiwan Dollar\nRussian ruble\nThai Baht\nRomanian Leu\nHungarian Forint\nPolish złoty\nIndian Rupee\nSelect currency type.\nNotify Assignees About New Orders\nMessenger \nEmail\nNotify Assignees when a new payment received.\nSend To Contact Successful Charge Receipt\nEmail\nTo notify a user about successful payment by e-mail, you have to tick the box in Manychat Payments and set this option up in your Stripe account by following this link\nTotal Orders:\n0\nPurchase History\nAvatar\nName\nDate\nOrder ID\nItem Price\nStatus\nItem Name\nAdditional Information\n